{"tid":1525362,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"幸存者偏差","createTime":"2019-08-31T23:15:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T03:39:21.000Z","uid":311143,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4cca872a2439e27acffa936a7c7f4e18d2174c84","tid":1525362,"uid":311143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T23:15:05.000Z","msg":"最近上YouTube見到「幸存者偏差」呢個理論，<br />\n大概係話好多人都只係搵成功既人士參考，<br />\n令到自己忽視左好多其他人失敗既因素，<br />\n令自己分析差左。<br />\n<br />\n同樣地，今次反送中示威入面，<br />\n我見到好多人都係分析左泰國，烏克蘭，黃背心，雨傘運動等比較出名既例子，<br />\n咁有冇一d比例少人知，但敗因值得我地參考既示威？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Qrc16Ha5Cgg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQrc16Ha5Cgg&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=5789a194\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Qrc16Ha5Cgg</a>"},{"pid":"67fe47e0956fd8fe392b11adf0f296dbe5d53dbb","tid":1525362,"uid":207470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T23:18:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021e6c6813e6c1f2f5c4b3d9888f2e2dc9e40bcd","tid":1525362,"uid":262952,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:36:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"abec11bf98794a750556f9d91a2a538cf38b700a","tid":1525362,"uid":234658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:07:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be009a6f51d5c8fd57d3a5fb8edbaf677f832cd0","tid":1525362,"uid":96169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:55:34.000Z","msg":"無心情呀<br />\n講啦"},{"pid":"b52796a4184fc7a21b4959ed42e7ffb425da1f0f","tid":1525362,"uid":267437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:12:25.000Z","msg":"8964其實好值得學習<br />\n好多野都發生緊"},{"pid":"069d38ad01e488cf4854889467aa83bd21c4517f","tid":1525362,"uid":257491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abec11bf98794a750556f9d91a2a538cf38b700a","tid":1525362,"uid":234658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"cit